module Core

### Defines the entity `MalformedUtf8Error`.
entity MalformedUtf8Error obeys Crashable
  ### Stores the index member value.
  index: U64
  ### Stores the reason member value.
  reason: Text

### Returns the result of `crash message`.
### :returns: The resulting `Text` value.
routine MalformedUtf8Error.crash_message() -> Text
  return f"Malformed UTF-8 at byte {me.index}: {me.reason}."
